#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:4
msgid "Object Origins"
msgstr "所有物体原心"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:6
msgid ""
"Each object has an origin point. The location of this point determines "
"where the object is located in 3D space. When an object is selected, a "
"small circle appears, denoting the origin point. The location of the origin "
"point is important when translating, rotating or scaling an object. See :"
"doc:`Pivot Points </editors/3dview/transform/transform_control/pivot_point/"
"index>` for more."
msgstr ""
"每个对象都有一个原点。此点的位置确定了在 3D 空间中的物体位置。当选定物体时，"
"将出现一个小圆圈，表示这个原点。变换、 旋转或缩放物体时，重要的起始点的位"
"置。查看 :doc:`轴心点 </editors/3dview/transform/transform_control/"
"pivot_point/index>`  获取更多信息。"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:13
msgid "Moving Object Centers"
msgstr "移动物体中心"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:15
msgid ""
"Object Centers can be moved to different positions through *3D View window "
"--> Transform --> Origin* (press :kbd:`T` to open panel):"
msgstr ""
"物体中心可以在3d视窗中被随意移动。菜单 从  *物体 --> 变换 --> 原点* 找到各种"
"命令，或者按 :kbd:`T` 键打开面板找到设置原点面板。"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:18
msgid "Geometry to Origin"
msgstr "几何中心到原点"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:19
msgid ""
"Move model to origin and this way origin of the object will also be at the "
"center of the object."
msgstr "把选择物体的几何中心对齐到物体原点位置。"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:21
msgid "Origin to Geometry"
msgstr "原点到几何中心"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:21
msgid ""
"Move origin to the center of the object and this way origin of the object "
"will also be at the center of the object."
msgstr "移动选择物体的原点到物体的几何中心位置。"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:23
msgid "Origin to 3D Cursor"
msgstr "原点到3d游标"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:24
msgid "Move origin of the model to the place of the 3D cursor."
msgstr "移动选择物体的原点到当前的3d游标位置。"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:27
msgid "Origin to Center of Mass"
msgstr "原点到质心"

#: ..\..\editors\3dview\transform\origns.rst:26
msgid "Move origin to calculated center of mass of model."
msgstr "移动选择物体的原点到物体质量中心位置。"
